">https://lihkg.com/thread/1631545/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d847c54b894023c3e5fdbf157190c117d6a90c74","tid":1632030,"uid":308282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:51:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb632c354508be40729bd498a2ce2cb1a28e38f1","tid":1632030,"uid":238975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:51:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a2b55b11b30203cb40e1db3410ced67737ff26","tid":1632030,"uid":315864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:51:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69e14bcbfc91360172a867de9bc851e6bad31fb9","tid":1632030,"uid":30907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:51:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc71c5b21aef8f876384c67645c9c4c728a1d7ce","tid":1632030,"uid":310065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:51:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6a09ea415a4b4f15a6bfd1a62c5de1b6a4dd1163","tid":1632030,"uid":30907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:51:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a0948ded66bf4cab673e8ee60efd261310cac26","tid":1632030,"uid":315864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:51:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4463bbce1c7a4ce0cf1f0c314146fc5726fef207","tid":1632030,"uid":310065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:51:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"99a25cb128eab767d65f343aeb70fdd483a8f0a3","tid":1632030,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"54f5964b25ab6932be83d667f2138eed2202436f","tid":1632030,"uid":238975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25fca821b1ce47a20756a8cb5b4f1d0fd61e4ee7","tid":1632030,"uid":310065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"67d52cf53c10e82f6ba5970a4a56eeed0cee1ec5","tid":1632030,"uid":308282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:24.000Z","msg":"未撚再比出樣個個po其他人<br />\n個個po要沉啊<br />\n保護當時人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb6076aaecc0464185cc7418ad1278cb8418688","tid":1632030,"uid":238975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1d3abbb12974715d324ce97c17c8e894a5f2cd","tid":1632030,"uid":105905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:45.000Z","msg":"紅日開庭????"},{"pid":"c801d84ef8ac553e47e1cec4d45be955b30dce1a","tid":1632030,"uid":238975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:56.000Z","msg":"推呢個！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851f32bbd4577f93e3bb381b3bd841ce77d94ec7","tid":1632030,"uid":308282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abea1b3ca17c2b240413c88c6d93c3a84243f944","tid":1632030,"uid":30907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2afce37cd51106bb082c6a3ca0ee9a98c1331308",